thread.title: BRIEF-Telekom Malaysia Posts Qtrly Net Profit Of ‍277​ Mln RGT

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Telekom Malaysia Posts Qtrly Net Profit Of ‍277​ Mln RGT
text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - Telekom Malaysia Bhd:
* QTRLY NET PROFIT ‍277​ MILLION RGT * QTRLY REVENUE 3.20 BILLION RGT * YEAR AGO QTRLY REVENUE 3.24 BILLION RGT; YEAR AGO QTRLY NET PROFIT 154.3 MILLION RGT
* DECLARES INTERIM DIVIDEND OF 12.1 SEN PER SHARE * SEES REVENUE GROWTH OF 3.5% TO 4.0% IN 2018‍​ * SEES "REVENUE GROWTH OF 3.5% TO 4.0% & EBIT GROWTH OF 3.5% TO 4.0%‍ IN THE MID-TERM"​ Source text : ( bit.ly/2CJP29o ) Further company coverage:
